This wind feels strange...
Sosuke, I'm starting the car!

29
00:10:02,924 --> 00:10:04,133
Did you find her?

30
00:10:09,722 --> 00:10:12,850
What, captured by a human?

31
00:10:15,937 --> 00:10:18,523
This is bad...very bad.

32
00:10:44,757 --> 00:10:46,509
Are you dead?

33
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,060
You're alive!

34
00:11:05,236 --> 00:11:09,365
Sosuke! I'm going to be late!

35
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:12,743
Lisa! I caught a goldfish.

36
00:11:12,869 --> 00:11:14,412
A goldfish?

37
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:16,914
Down by the rocks.

38
00:11:42,732 --> 00:11:46,110
I'm sorry, but you can't
use weed killer here.

39
00:11:48,738 --> 00:11:54,535
Heavens no! This is pure sea water.
It keeps me humidified.

40
00:11:54,619 --> 00:11:57,371
As long as
it's not weed killer.

41
00:11:57,830 --> 00:11:59,165
Good day!

42
00:12:07,173 --> 00:12:09,258
This is very bad.

43
00:12:11,969 --> 00:12:13,679
What a creepy guy.

44
00:12:13,804 --> 00:12:17,058
But don't you say that
about strangers, Sosuke.

45
00:12:17,141 --> 00:12:18,643
I won't.

46
00:12:18,726 --> 00:12:21,312
Are you taking
that to school?

47
00:12:22,188 --> 00:12:23,773
Won't the teacher complain?

48
00:12:24,106 --> 00:12:27,818
Don't worry,
I'll take care of you.

49
00:12:27,985 --> 00:12:29,487
She's cute!

50
00:12:36,285 --> 00:12:38,162
They're using the dry dock.

51
00:12:39,705 --> 00:12:42,291
Here, eat this
before we get there.

52
00:12:43,501 --> 00:12:45,461
Maybe she's hungry.

53
00:12:46,337 --> 00:12:47,630
Want some?

54
00:12:49,006 --> 00:12:51,300
Hey, my cut is gone!

55
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:57,306
I'm going to call her Ponyo.

56
00:12:57,974 --> 00:13:01,018
She's really special!
She can do magic.

57
00:13:01,644 --> 00:13:04,355
She fixed my cut.

58
00:13:14,532 --> 00:13:16,534
Want some ham?

59
00:13:31,465 --> 00:13:35,469
- Ponyo likes ham, Lisa!
- That makes two of us.

60
00:13:58,951 --> 00:14:00,536
Oh no...

61
00:14:03,247 --> 00:14:04,874
Disgusting!

62
00:14:05,166 --> 00:14:06,917
Hurry, Lisa!

63
00:14:15,843 --> 00:14:18,429
Such filth! Intolerable!

64
00:14:20,514 --> 00:14:21,932
Good morning!

65
00:14:28,689 --> 00:14:31,359
Look, Ponyo.
There's our house.

66
00:14:52,671 --> 00:14:54,840
- I'll drop you here.
- Okay.

67
00:14:54,965 --> 00:14:56,008
Have fun.

68
00:14:56,133 --> 00:14:57,718
See you.

69
00:14:59,053 --> 00:15:00,554
Morning.
Sorry I'm late.

70
00:15:00,638 --> 00:15:02,556
Could you get
Noriko's wheelchair?

71
00:15:18,114 --> 00:15:19,824
Good morning, Sosuke.

72
00:15:19,907 --> 00:15:22,701
I'm busy, Yoshie.
Talk to you later.

73
00:15:22,827 --> 00:15:24,078
