The tsunami is here!

144
00:20:57,828 --> 00:20:59,329
What's wrong, Toki?

145
00:20:59,413 --> 00:21:01,915
Just look at my clothes!

146
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:11,175
Sosuke!

147
00:21:16,180 --> 00:21:18,223
Sosuke!

148
00:21:24,104 --> 00:21:26,023
Sosuke!

149
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,901
Come back here and apologize!

150
00:21:38,202 --> 00:21:41,997
Don't worry, I'll protect you.

151
00:21:43,916 --> 00:21:45,209
Sosuke.

152
00:21:48,796 --> 00:21:50,339
Sosuke.

153
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,677
Ponyo!

154
00:21:58,138 --> 00:22:00,474
Ponyo. Sosuke.

155
00:22:01,141 --> 00:22:03,060
Ponyo... loves...

156
00:22:03,727 --> 00:22:05,270
...Sosuke!

157
00:22:10,901 --> 00:22:12,277
I love you too.

158
00:22:12,861 --> 00:22:15,364
Ponyo loves Sosuke!

159
00:22:56,071 --> 00:22:57,489
Ponyo!

160
00:22:58,907 --> 00:23:01,618
Ponyo!

161
00:23:06,039 --> 00:23:07,958
Ponyo!

162
00:23:09,793 --> 00:23:11,879
Sosuke!

163
00:23:13,005 --> 00:23:15,007
Ponyo!

164
00:24:16,568 --> 00:24:19,738
Listen, Sosuke.
Maybe it was fate.

165
00:24:19,863 --> 00:24:22,115
It just can't be helped.

166
00:24:23,033 --> 00:24:25,035
Ponyo was born in the sea.

167
00:24:25,118 --> 00:24:27,204
She went back home,
that's all.

168
00:24:27,746 --> 00:24:31,541
Anyway, let's hope
that creepy guy is gone.

169
00:24:32,501 --> 00:24:33,543
One lick?

170
00:24:34,711 --> 00:24:36,088
Hurry, it's melting!

171
00:24:39,508 --> 00:24:40,884
Not bad!

172
00:24:46,014 --> 00:24:49,351
Cheer up.
Koichi will be home tonight.

173
00:24:50,394 --> 00:24:53,522
He'll be disappointed
if you're feeling down.

174
00:25:19,715 --> 00:25:22,092
No more ocean today, okay?

175
00:25:49,244 --> 00:25:50,912
Sosuke?

176
00:25:51,705 --> 00:25:53,290
Time to come inside.

177
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:58,295
Do you think this bucket
will help Ponyo find us?

178
00:25:58,670 --> 00:26:01,798
There's only one way
to find out.

179
00:26:15,896 --> 00:26:19,524
Can you get that, Sosuke?
It must be Koichi.

180
00:26:21,818 --> 00:26:23,070
Hello?

181
00:26:23,153 --> 00:26:24,988
Yes, it's me.

182
00:26:25,697 --> 00:26:27,657
<i>Yes, I'm fine.</i>

183
00:26:27,783 --> 00:26:32,120
I can't get back tonight.
I'll signal when I'm offshore.

184
00:26:32,329 --> 00:26:34,623
Okay. Here's Lisa.

185
00:26:36,166 --> 00:26:39,127
Koichi? Yes...
What?!

186
00:26:39,836 --> 00:26:42,130
Can't you get out of it?

187
00:26:42,214 --> 00:26:46,009
Fine...leave your wife
and son up on the cliff!

188
00:26:46,218 --> 00:26:47,844
I give up!

189
00:26:51,348 --> 00:26:52,682
Why bother?

190
00:26:53,225 --> 00:26:55,310
C'mon Sosuke,
let's eat out!

191
00:26:56,436 --> 00:26:58,146
I want to eat here.

192
00:27:26,842 --> 00:27:27,884
There he is!

193
00:27:28,009 --> 00:27:30,846
Turn off the lights, Lisa.

194
00:27:54,744 --> 00:27:58,748
It's Sosuke! He's a genius.
Only five years old.

195
00:27:58,874 --> 00:28:00,750
Your wife must be upset.

196
00:28:05,338 --> 00:28:08,884
He says he's sorry.

